{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, they helped themselves, as well, because then they did not have to rush, rush, rush all the time, but they continued to go at a pretty good pace anyway, which all of us have to do.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I'm grateful to the-- particularly the French prisoners who-- who backed us so loyally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, thank you for reminding me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Indeed, I forgot that part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the time came for me to visit the Continental Gummi-Werke, and the general manager of engineering took-- took us around the premises, the huge yard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remembered exactly where our camp was located, and I told him that the electric wire fences were over there, and that little church, where actually I met their board of directors who invited me to this event at the factory, because they heard me speak at the unveiling of this monument.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just learned that the Continental Gummi-Werke still does not recognize the fact that there were slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, well, it's just in time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I gave a little speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in it, I said, that I understand that the Continental Gummi-Werke to date does not acknowledge the fact that they had slave laborers during the war, but I was one who was a slave laborer here, at the Continental Gummi-Werke, at the age of 15, and that I would like to visit the factory while I am in Hannover, whether I am invited or not.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And apparently they had their spies there, and-- and while we had a little reception in that church, which we could see from the grounds of the factory-- I remembered very well.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very charming-- charming church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's a very old, historical church.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
